## üéØ Testing Scenarios

### Tenant Switching
1. Start in Organization A
2. Click tenant dropdown
3. Select Organization B
4. Data updates to show Org B's leads/calls

### Role Switching
1. Start as Admin (see "Add Lead" button)
2. Click role dropdown
3. Select Agent
4. "Add Lead" button disappears (permission denied)

### Filtering
1. Open Leads module
2. Click status filter
3. Select "New" status
4. Table updates instantly showing only new leads

### Permission Checks
1. As Agent: No edit buttons visible
2. As Admin: Edit buttons visible everywhere
3. Switch to Agent: UI updates immediately

