## üîß How to Use This Project

### For Interview/Submission
1. Copy all files to your project folder
2. Run `npm install`
3. Run `npm run dev`
4. Show the working application
5. Walk through the code with the interviewer

### To Customize
1. Change mock data in `src/utils/mockData.js`
2. Modify colors in `tailwind.config.js`
3. Add new permissions in `src/utils/permissions.js`
4. Create new components in `src/components/`

### To Deploy
1. Run `npm run build` (creates `dist/` folder)
2. Upload `dist/` to hosting service
3. Or use services like Vercel, Netlify, GitHub Pages

